RE Equalizer player is exactly what I was looking for. This music player also features 10 band eq, audio effects such as Bass boost and surround and balance control. About the sound quality, this music player beats other apps like Poweramp, jetaudio etc. User interface is easy to setup and use. The style of user interface is very similar to Spotify and YouTube music although this is an offline music player. Despite simplicity, it also features very advanced options like crossfading etc. Best!

Equipped with a robust sound engine and an array of sound features, the RE Equalizer player is the best music app on the play store now. The UI is beautiful and clean providing dynamic control over the media library and sound quality. All audio files can easily be accessed and navigated in the uniquely designed media library. The built-in equalizer and the additional sound features are finely-tuned allowing users to tweak the sound quality to their preference. Thanks for the amazing experience.

I guess I am just lucky enough to find this cool music app and special thanks to the developers.
